text: Keiko Nakagomi (中込恵子, Nakagomi Keiko, born 12 June 1970) is a Japanese archer. Nakagomi competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Keiko NakagomiKeiko NAKAGOMI == References == Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese archers Category:Olympians for Japan Category:Sportspeople from Tokyo
